description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Years End Row' from the channel Dani Hansen.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn. The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no oneâ€™s watching and feel amazing..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: Celebrate the end of 2022 and share what you're looking forward to in 2023 with Dani in Tampa through 45-second intervals.
